msgid "The pin mode, either `Pin.IN` (default) or `Pin.OUT`."
msgstr "引脚模式，可以是 `Pin.IN`（默认）或 `Pin.OUT`。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:116 3b548784d415498a8024e498ac14db80
msgid ""
"The initial value to set for the pin if in `OUT` mode. Use `None` for no "
"initial value."
