msgid "The mode of the pin, either `Pin.IN` (default) or `Pin.OUT`."
msgstr "引脚的模式，可以是 `Pin.IN`（默认）或 `Pin.OUT`。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:133 a5e1edf823b147e59756bff802f0d7a0
msgid "Optional initial value for the pin, 0 or 1."
msgstr "引脚的可选初始值，0 或 1。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:145 27680382d3e64487837b5971990cf99f
msgid "Reinitialize the pin with a new mode or value."
msgstr "使用新的模式或值重新初始化引脚。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:147 1659ac8107c54a15b29f0fcf2310f2ee
msgid "New mode for the pin, `Pin.IN` (default) or `Pin.OUT`."
msgstr "引脚的新模式：`Pin.IN`（默认）或 `Pin.OUT`。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:148 42b60e24a81c452caea4d1a3711ad99e
msgid "New value for the pin, 0 or 1."
msgstr "引脚的新值，0 或 1。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:153 00b74ea5601f4c0a9fff3870a20b5bbe
msgid "Get or set the digital value of the pin."
msgstr "获取或设置引脚的数字值。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:155 353d319b0508411884f7c995a8accc48
msgid ""
"If no arguments are passed, the method returns the current value of the "
"pin. If one argument is passed, it sets the pin to the specified value."
msgstr "如果未传入参数，该方法将返回引脚的当前值。如果传入一个参数，则将引脚设置为指定值。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:158 f585003868d546c1bf718664829dda26
msgid "Optional argument to set the pin value."
msgstr "用于设置引脚值的可选参数。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:163 f8fca8d13f014a28a1ce29a676df455b
msgid "Set the pin to a high state (1)."
msgstr "将引脚设置为高电平状态 (1)。"

#: ../../source/unit/extio.rst:168 01e5d04736574ce38c237f39fd4007e9
msgid "Set the pin to a low state (0)."
msgstr "将引脚设置为低电平状态（0）。"

